{"word":"G3063 - λοιπόν - loipón - loy-pon' - Besides","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λοιπόν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">loipón</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">loy-pon'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Besides</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb Neuter / வினையடை (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"இனி - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. remaining, the rest"},{"paragraph":"2. hereafter, for the future, henceforth"},{"paragraph":"3. at last, already"},{"paragraph":"4. for the rest, besides, moreover"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter singular of the same as <a href=\"#/G3062 - λοιποί - loipoí - loy-poy'/3062\">G3062</a>; something <i>remaining</i> (adverb): - besides, finally, furthermore, (from) henceforth, moreover, now, + it remaineth, then.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}